Body:
I am trying to run end-to-end sample example from Google IoT Cloud

https://cloud.google.com/iot/docs/samples/end-to-end-sample

Issue :

I am not receiving any data in the server ("cloudiot_pubsub_example_server.py") from pub/sub subscription. I can see data in the pub/sub by pulling messages. I am able to pull in the console also using "gcloud pubsub subscriptions pull --auto-ack projects/applied-grove-246108/subscriptions/my-subscription". But not able to receive through server.

Below is the the server command am trying.

python cloudiot_pubsub_example_server.py --project_id=applied-grove-246108 --pubsub_subscription=projects/applied-grove-246108/subscriptions/my-subscription --service_account_json=service_account.json

Any help much appreciated.

"
